#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn23.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:0.2"
msgid "3. Āyācanavagga "
msgstr "3. Appeals "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:0.3"
msgid "23–33. Mārādisuttaekādasaka "
msgstr "23–33. Eleven Discourses on Māra, Etc. "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:1.3"
msgid "“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, māro; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo. "
msgstr "“Rādha, you should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever is Māra. "

msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.2"
msgid "Ko ca, rādha, māro? "
msgstr "And what is Māra? "

msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.3"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, māro; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo. "
msgstr "Form is Māra. You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.4"
msgid "Vedanā māro; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.5"
msgid "saññā māro; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.6"
msgid "saṅkhārā māro; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.7"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ māro; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Consciousness is Māra. You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for it. "

msgctxt "sn23.23-33:2.8"
msgid "yo kho, rādha, māro; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo”ti. "
msgstr "You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever is Māra.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:3.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, māradhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo … pe …. (2) "
msgstr "“You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever is of Māra-like nature …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.199, sc4
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:4.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, rādha, aniccaṃ … pe …. (3) "
msgstr "“… impermanent …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:5.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, aniccadhammo … pe …. (4) "
msgstr "“… naturally impermanent …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:6.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, rādha, dukkhaṃ … pe …. (5) "
msgstr "“… suffering …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:7.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, dukkhadhammo … pe …. (6) "
msgstr "“… things that entail suffering …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:8.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, anattā … pe …. (7) "
msgstr "“… not-self …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:9.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, anattadhammo … pe …. (8) "
msgstr "“… naturally not-self …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:10.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, khayadhammo … pe …. (9) "
msgstr "“… liable to end …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:11.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, vayadhammo … pe …. (10) "
msgstr "“… liable to vanish …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "sn23.23-33:12.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, samudayadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo … pe …. (11) "
msgstr "“… liable to originate …”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
